Add a sticky "New Thought" button at the bottom of the desktop sidebar in `Sidebar.tsx`. It calls `useStore.getState().openQuickAdd()` on click, stays always visible via `sticky bottom-0`, and is hidden on mobile (`hidden md:block`) since the `MobileFAB` handles that. The design spec in `design/reli_ai_chat_panel/code.html:108-113` defines the exact styling.

