- `Sidebar.tsx:861` — `hidden md:block` for desktop-only elements
- `store.ts:1536` + `App.tsx:211` — `openQuickAdd` already fully wired end-to-end, nothing new needed

### Risks

- Screenshot tests will fail until regenerated (expected — run `test:screenshots:update`, visually verify, then `test:screenshots`)

